            115.2528255,-8.5222661,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>2. Grazing on the Green</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6mhQQKaS_xXN-nzOXGsBt1tY2tWbHmy7wVJT6Pf-WBuBStGqjMcoBh30l5yt1ummQI9pWmLkhsRYdcYBO4XD2K1tJ7GPgkc6glW_j8lbe1pH3v6z0xUG6CHju2z6_1-O_a0CQGZdYB5NMwRiFGDT6PB7c-8S5lOfiGNDTTa_eSkqFYm_KJ1YqHLAIYtXzg1SLjT9P51ah6o-gb-RvYphosh2h3lBhhRf3kA9vCQwVtzzUWFpyuIiO_-Qw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>【Travelors' Choice 2023】<br><br>在草坪上享用地中海美食 - Finns VIP 海灘俱樂部獨有的特色；在修剪整齊的海濱草坪上享受野餐。週三至週日下午 3 點開放野餐設施，包括毯子和枕頭！<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
