      <Placemark>
        <name>4. Ivy Cafe</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7FbQkp-F5Im_KDPC05-DWATx5FYDarveN15ISs2jCum0fkkTc0gYbKIpoOJEpbzcE2xN5zi7fTVn9J9j2mAIBibFfC8qUxfkc5vJq1ED9wHJLVayC3TRo7oC1bBQKPyI-oJMNjwfQVZHpOWNHMCSZkw6vlnOOSVyaQwB2ks30kP8NHIv2YY-z9NzEsbprpTgo5zKwLDxIIDScegjKwwBvSLmKC4OdpErssALOnzMU1R0HzRH5AGyNHo-Q?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Ivy 是一家舒適的餐廳，供應由最新鮮的當地食材製成的新鮮、健康和美味的食物，為您的身心提供能量。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
