      <Placemark>
        <name>5. Tanah Liat</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4foUhVQtt_z5U_QainYwN5fir08wCEH4ZUGurzLvCac06MdB97y3XrmHBlNGwuUo75kFtqfRqz7cFMLzFk3Dvpc9xHSiTD3R27ygITcWxWK1pUJf4BChf2-lG7nSX8x0HYKfauQ9SvUv-LTZoymKrNePhwTTwn9w-Drtra-do7SFtL0uQeG3gZRVm2OFLEP2K-JWoLrAJcRaK7HyPBuqTZQKm5mRRC5nZSlpkeRbbkIobOrIUXQrvgqjU?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Tanah Liat 白天是陶器工作室和烹飪實驗室，晚上則搖身一變，成為一家以藝術和手工藝為靈感的餐廳，專注於體驗式美食，突出巴厘島採購的新鮮時令海鮮和植物性美食。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4foUhVQtt_z5U_QainYwN5fir08wCEH4ZUGurzLvCac06MdB97y3XrmHBlNGwuUo75kFtqfRqz7cFMLzFk3Dvpc9xHSiTD3R27ygITcWxWK1pUJf4BChf2-lG7nSX8x0HYKfauQ9SvUv-LTZoymKrNePhwTTwn9w-Drtra-do7SFtL0uQeG3gZRVm2OFLEP2K-JWoLrAJcRaK7HyPBuqTZQKm5mRRC5nZSlpkeRbbkIobOrIUXQrvgqjU?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
