      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>6. Kulkul Beach House</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4_BxBqHIVsWDKENRYcCt5I53Mf25rWeAlxZVv3cg3P7CrtHL9x7j4ID63cfDxK1CxQgdX-ndnx_O0N6x4VbBhrZ42RUuDrAd4Y3-55vVTK6XRA6t-9QizlF4Y_75jr0qXovgi5cWXkQWtLA_hScvdRsaFKRiHCuha0JEXpA5HD3R5JkGJ3KUHZHv4w_aqyQo2_NhIT6agfIl5Kq8zJp1_VBxfCQjk8maX1U_h3UNLEfEI0o6yGnp3mxio?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Kulkul 是一座別緻而悠閒的海濱別墅，最近重新開放，在充滿異國情調的努沙杜瓦海灘上可以欣賞到印度洋的最佳景觀。 Kulkul 提供輕鬆的氛圍，並在泳池旁提供小屋。全天菜單和雞尾酒專注於零浪費餐飲和以當地食材烹製的創意菜單。 Kulkul 鼓勵客人全天和晚上休閒放鬆，是體驗峇裡島海灘寧靜氛圍的完美目的地。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4_BxBqHIVsWDKENRYcCt5I53Mf25rWeAlxZVv3cg3P7CrtHL9x7j4ID63cfDxK1CxQgdX-ndnx_O0N6x4VbBhrZ42RUuDrAd4Y3-55vVTK6XRA6t-9QizlF4Y_75jr0qXovgi5cWXkQWtLA_hScvdRsaFKRiHCuha0JEXpA5HD3R5JkGJ3KUHZHv4w_aqyQo2_NhIT6agfIl5Kq8zJp1_VBxfCQjk8maX1U_h3UNLEfEI0o6yGnp3mxio?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2329138,-8.7971009,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[7. Sleeping Gajah Kitchen & Lounge]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5l3nZrHZ5YOULMUfyZnZBIr-gYmK5rYJ8P1MIT1RSYgivyEj0-h8ZoyBX2BYtqRyR0iFkn2kpATFiodhz4Cv9KAUGYcSyMOmi7FPZ_8ZhSU-C1jioUexDbK57I2-bYg5aHhijtRUvBdbIQWJPJ1_vFBxTEOc88TPW_24Y-hC5DkP0hGJqXQCU7oF9RmHLQYlihGtpl2E05k-ySmoOHMIpfad6_3IKOLOMitdarkr2a3KVUidRWHdq-lnE?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>【Travelors' Choice 2023】<br><br>露天餐廳可容納 70 個座位，您可以欣賞到山丘全景和烏達河的自然聲音。我們的早餐、午餐和晚餐均採用休閒輕鬆的用餐方式，旨在以優質美食滿足您的口味。我們提供各種菜餚，如一般印尼菜、西餐，其中以我們的招牌菜為特色。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5l3nZrHZ5YOULMUfyZnZBIr-gYmK5rYJ8P1MIT1RSYgivyEj0-h8ZoyBX2BYtqRyR0iFkn2kpATFiodhz4Cv9KAUGYcSyMOmi7FPZ_8ZhSU-C1jioUexDbK57I2-bYg5aHhijtRUvBdbIQWJPJ1_vFBxTEOc88TPW_24Y-hC5DkP0hGJqXQCU7oF9RmHLQYlihGtpl2E05k-ySmoOHMIpfad6_3IKOLOMitdarkr2a3KVUidRWHdq-lnE?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
