      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>10. Bai Yun Hot Pot</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6zGf9zyIqcYY-eQfoWzBnpFdhpKfEbf0WIUJLpXDiyXS6aaTmxVH7qne62Ioshi8dVnc2Mar5_WkjXmRV3qwSCVH6Spelu927HSyFrirKjdKR_FafDY07xjj7ORu8N9z6AQFnrWP57fyE4X2hDHC7bdolEr5VZss-uZ0phQmVH_jA1b9umHzKhA_ZcCNfDgX07mJ053mr-FXBweAS6QzweDRwM4EMagtD6gaacXkXOyEoCeEOovUzE7No?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>【Travelors' Choice 2023 Best of the Best】<br><br>從蒙古到中國，如今又風靡東南亞，巴厘島阿普爾瓦凱賓斯基酒店最新的餐飲場所——白雲，可以享受火鍋歡樂的用餐體驗。白雲在漢語中意為“白雲”，與這家餐廳的餐飲理念產生共鳴。當火鍋產生熱量時，空氣中飄浮著蒸汽，就像白雲一樣。營業時間: 點心: 12:00 - 16:00 火鍋: 16:00 - 22:00<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6zGf9zyIqcYY-eQfoWzBnpFdhpKfEbf0WIUJLpXDiyXS6aaTmxVH7qne62Ioshi8dVnc2Mar5_WkjXmRV3qwSCVH6Spelu927HSyFrirKjdKR_FafDY07xjj7ORu8N9z6AQFnrWP57fyE4X2hDHC7bdolEr5VZss-uZ0phQmVH_jA1b9umHzKhA_ZcCNfDgX07mJ053mr-FXBweAS6QzweDRwM4EMagtD6gaacXkXOyEoCeEOovUzE7No?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
