      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>11. Hiiragi Restaurant</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4S49VZnkzTZczi7OHmih8eBny_8R3pbPLop2cI9qg6ibvMw8Ul7OyGCLzlqbKym0h6SuyzDv0naSQCKuRtLjQi4yObo0G267ojIca_V3miLngyOatju49KcIEkg3vJsbM66qWNOZwWsrZj7LF4wOexFQVWu09axrxgK7bXVlijhdc2jPHGg2Y02VHWs_s9ssQ5mxdcPSAdd0ouh0vxMFjvs33ucRZIPLMqwRxR4xvqC36r_BMfofUSDhc?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>讓自己沉浸在融合和品味的境界中，日本和秘魯烹飪傳統的無縫融合孕育出真正非凡的東西。加入我們，享受無與倫比的用餐體驗。我們全天供應輕鬆的菜單，供應時間為上午 7 點至下午 6 點，提供各種令人愉悅的均衡且美味的菜餚，均採用新鮮的當地食材精心製作。下午 6 點至晚上 11 點，我們的菜單提供各種精美菜餚，精心烹製，體現了日經美食的真正精髓。讓我們帶您進入一個充滿融合和風味的境界。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4S49VZnkzTZczi7OHmih8eBny_8R3pbPLop2cI9qg6ibvMw8Ul7OyGCLzlqbKym0h6SuyzDv0naSQCKuRtLjQi4yObo0G267ojIca_V3miLngyOatju49KcIEkg3vJsbM66qWNOZwWsrZj7LF4wOexFQVWu09axrxgK7bXVlijhdc2jPHGg2Y02VHWs_s9ssQ5mxdcPSAdd0ouh0vxMFjvs33ucRZIPLMqwRxR4xvqC36r_BMfofUSDhc?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
