      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>14. St Tropez Bali</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6OcsqImNCyJwLJp0L4Wq2h77nWklEfj_a4GQnHOcFfLzCifJn0ArNJADQT9VYA4lw8thx3CSrSWsv6JWxF7Ze7TCB75Gyc6WIk7hgdeVjc1Vt9KvWDtV6_BaYlmjCUQ3q6UIXfY0Tbh2dA7pz58TKyNiQ_xtW__ESJqUyBy65B-0YeGgIOS2sOoOMSengbO0cetwkw-LpRVLjdM4FlfAD4F0Eb1l-_XbyJufb6uC7Ix_9yPdeXcICdhJs?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>位於世界最佳海灘俱樂部，加入我們的聖特羅佩，享用世界一流的地中海美食和美味飲料。來享用午餐、日落、晚餐，並觀看我們的現場表演和娛樂活動的派對。用餐、跳舞，享受適合所有年齡層的難忘體驗。很快在聖特羅佩再見！<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6OcsqImNCyJwLJp0L4Wq2h77nWklEfj_a4GQnHOcFfLzCifJn0ArNJADQT9VYA4lw8thx3CSrSWsv6JWxF7Ze7TCB75Gyc6WIk7hgdeVjc1Vt9KvWDtV6_BaYlmjCUQ3q6UIXfY0Tbh2dA7pz58TKyNiQ_xtW__ESJqUyBy65B-0YeGgIOS2sOoOMSengbO0cetwkw-LpRVLjdM4FlfAD4F0Eb1l-_XbyJufb6uC7Ix_9yPdeXcICdhJs?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
