      <Placemark>
        <name>17. Kemangi Ubud Resto</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X59w7-lJCEGAtUS8lzyjcFxLSfhfXITJEWppKOIhxLK5VV5b0WduQYuutwZfNZ_F1X5E2GfM2myQXJMpDortJYlX7hXne7M5jtqjzXSECOXGiD72_o89wF1IdaGqXjrYDJh7WJQyD9fU2IQPJg-MasZb_XV1_RLzJ3Yped5Fpme0KVrnKzOECic9v2gEEqIoN7Q-No3KSj2ImQa9A6fD41MgcQ9EFaNPtiTlCibXFbDnPxR8fyPUsfbSrc?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>在烏布市中心的 Kemangi Ubud Resto 餐廳，盡情享受充滿異國風味的正宗巴厘島和國際菜餚的美食之旅。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
