      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>18. Seminyak Kitchen</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X52DIyZgVvAhF7lsiRPBUNbtmZnFa56km-7iWeHW7oAmeFt_zTiO1MXU-qouaYAlLabQwLcVC0jJxaH1kGgP3sk3KcFmrITZRvnk0-oE2uiWqy2hg0kJ18EzfJTm9RB_LV30QZA1n20EDjfnlgc3dhZVzjWaBUFozi4XhNj0nPTzxyfYB9TTRvzc8as2Gb9F2LbH3ErmH-4CKV7X97OV7iNyCZIfqmWqZmmaWhvqij1u8eyPyKoKlVvcMw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>【Travelors' Choice 2023】<br><br>水明漾廚房提供多種當地最受歡迎的亞洲和國際菜餚，我們才華橫溢的廚師在我們的開放式廚房中在您眼前展示他們的技能。最重要的是，我們訓練有素且細心的團隊將確保您在水明漾中心享受難忘的用餐體驗。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X52DIyZgVvAhF7lsiRPBUNbtmZnFa56km-7iWeHW7oAmeFt_zTiO1MXU-qouaYAlLabQwLcVC0jJxaH1kGgP3sk3KcFmrITZRvnk0-oE2uiWqy2hg0kJ18EzfJTm9RB_LV30QZA1n20EDjfnlgc3dhZVzjWaBUFozi4XhNj0nPTzxyfYB9TTRvzc8as2Gb9F2LbH3ErmH-4CKV7X97OV7iNyCZIfqmWqZmmaWhvqij1u8eyPyKoKlVvcMw?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.162374,-8.691726,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>19. Bee Cafe Bali</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4rwLEKPYURgcMZl82RsSu9Bm-6STJjFkkfViuGV0MoZyCSdkTFlt7TXPAoWg2BJJ1HtwF-TLthFr0XvysnH9wQSTw_dcSONR-MQ3OM7Bxhbsu9pbbbAObjiKMXXyMzT47RY8cy7yUw25xpg3xWahkSPRyimdOhicW5-iVUfB9ECcdDp19P_xA5dcLq__OtrDGGS1ufKq-KQ9jXNoE-hh4Bvh4VARrfVqPJJ1VgVxj2a6SkbYFZTiJ6_As?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>【Travelors' Choice 2023】<br><br>蜜蜂咖啡館 (Bee Café) 坐擁鬱鬱蔥蔥的稻田美景，其建造時考慮了 Wantilan Subak（灌溉社區住宅）。這裡是所有農民勞作後聚集休息吃飯的地方。因此，如果您正在尋找正宗的巴厘島體驗，同時享受美味的印尼美食，那麼這裡就是您的最佳選擇。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4rwLEKPYURgcMZl82RsSu9Bm-6STJjFkkfViuGV0MoZyCSdkTFlt7TXPAoWg2BJJ1HtwF-TLthFr0XvysnH9wQSTw_dcSONR-MQ3OM7Bxhbsu9pbbbAObjiKMXXyMzT47RY8cy7yUw25xpg3xWahkSPRyimdOhicW5-iVUfB9ECcdDp19P_xA5dcLq__OtrDGGS1ufKq-KQ9jXNoE-hh4Bvh4VARrfVqPJJ1VgVxj2a6SkbYFZTiJ6_As?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2741602,-8.5169923,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>20. Herb Library Bali</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7f87jTDNj86VfsrWkmwfoGHo6P_gGOQpX3-tK88_GP3BYI0BBCGb4LZ8rA2REu7bbWcZ1bG_VGRbgNAb_kI7jZ9pW86k_3baEMdLl1TkKHI9NQ05Ks0ck217LkGWpCqUmKnbNwSPBYtywCrVA7ibQr7Cd8MFxfiVcBgrlHGhTOtYFzQBvXOY6qNP_wXO7VOKVkfZxl6SkgH-cG0lvzhiMc0d4v3li0knYCXqF7mGHwACNYWKNSiR4wESI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>【Travelors' Choice 2023 Best of the Best】<br><br>它提供由生食倡導者精心製作且營養均衡的菜單。與度假村的阿育吠陀健康理念相得益彰。明確聚焦在植物性美食以及可持續養殖的雞肉和魚。<br><br>介紹文：https://gobaligo.id/go/bali-vegan-guide]]></description>
